            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffffffa6>暴擊傷害提升</color> <color=#37ffff>20%/25%/30%/35%/40%</color> <color=#ffffffa6>；生命之契的數值增加時，裝備者造成的傷害提升</color> <color=#37ffff>16%/20%/24%/28%/32%</color> <color=#ffffffa6>。該效果持續6秒，至多疊加3次。</color>"
          }
        ]
